title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Sim Update 12 - new build available
description:
In this video we will have a look at what has been fixed in the new build which has just been made available for Sim Update 12. In this build new fixes can be found for several aircrafts as well as some generic fixes.

The full list of fixes can be found via the link below:
